      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this dependable and character-filled ride! This car is a true workhorse that has been well-loved and is ready for its next chapter. While it shows some honest signs of use and a few cosmetic imperfections consistent with its age, it remains a solid and functional choice for anyone looking for a reliable daily driver at a great value!",
