    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind a bit of character. The exterior shows noticeable signs of age, including several scuffs on the bumpers, some clear coat peeling on the trunk, and a few small dings along the passenger side. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, it runs and drives, though it will likely need new brake pads and a suspension tune-up in the near future. It's an honest car at a fair price for someone looking for affordable transportation.",
