      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is an absolute gem\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it looks and drives just like it did when it first left the showroom. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and kept in tip-top shape, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
