    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD is a masterclass in lightweight engineering and rotary performance. It features the legendary 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged engine, delivering linear power delivery and maintaining exceptional compression across both rotors. The chassis boasts a perfect 50/50 weight distribution, supported by an all-aluminum double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen limited-slip differential for superior lateral grip. This specimen remains in an unmolested state, with original intake plumbing and factory-spec heat shielding intact. Every gear engagement in the five-speed manual transmission is tactile and precise, reflecting its meticulous maintenance history. A true survivor for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
